{"tid":1701277,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(分化敵人為上策) 藍衫跑到死，白衫嘆冷氣","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T00:56:15.000Z","uid":222970,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb058d6467410038dc2d6d412cf1c4f722a8f0f","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2334001953353281?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2334001953353281%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=a0981a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2334001953353281?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n有片 <br />\n<br />\n藍衫跑到死，白衫嘆冷氣<br />\n<br />\n請大家出黎到試下叫呢個口號<br />\n<br />\n拉一派打一派 係戰略 <br />\n<br />\n呢d唔係洗白 請唔好睇到咁表面<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n【白衫對話】 藍衫話：唔岩聽咩？我問下林sir睇下岩唔岩例先囉！ 咁岩聽嘛sir<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ccef027aaa1304db01ba64cd4c9366361ae5848","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"毛主席<br />\n<br />\n一方面要集中自己，另一方面要分散敵人。兩個方面合在一起，敵之強勢就變成弱勢，我之弱勢就變成強勢。經過這樣的縱橫捭闔，本來是敵強我弱的局勢，就變成了我強敵弱的局勢。這是毛澤東在戰場上和政壇上能夠以弱勝強，立於不敗之地的根本訣竅。"},{"pid":"f971b741bef97787f2ed2ba6094793d082815841","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"毛澤東的天才不僅表現在他善於團結聯合一切可以團結聯合的朋友，而且表現在他善於發現敵人營壘內部的縫隙。敵人不是清一色的，因此敵人營壘內部也有矛盾，不是鐵板一塊，其中有強有弱，有主有次，有不太堅決、動搖不定的，也有頑固不化，不打不倒的。"},{"pid":"9c8734fc835f9d10585cc77a742027aa706edbf8","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"一個一個地消滅敵人，是毛澤東統戰謀略中的另一核心精神，並且正好與&ldquo;團結一切可以團結的人&rdquo;相對應。將一切可以團結的人都集聚在自己周圍，同時將敵人加以分割，一個一個地消滅，這樣，就沒有戰勝不了的敵人，就沒有任何敵人可以戰勝自己。"},{"pid":"6ff3254a659465d327a37f8c2b15d44db919caa5","tid":1701277,"uid":56084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"咪傻 藍衫不知幾enjoy出黎打你"},{"pid":"c3f425a1aa08a9b4d08872d8f8cc90a4dae45217","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01819d4ef73aed293b134dcb996cfe1aec8c433","tid":1701277,"uid":132572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"就係分撚左先打得咁仆街<br />\nd白衫完全控制唔到<br />\n之前成鳩日話內鬨<br />\n點知其實係d散仔屌鳩d白衫唔放開手比人打<br />\ne加成功分化班散仔 不受上面控制"},{"pid":"25bd43189dbeb8ac129562db3bcceea430159834","tid":1701277,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"衣家好似係藍衫控制白衫"},{"pid":"d2018725aa2fcd0869e4684c3b3434288b11e543","tid":1701277,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b83c27abdad01e79c43b4f005f7a2a506dbaa8","tid":1701277,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"散仔衝鋒 大sir領功"},{"pid":"d96d3a5e32513d77c3af2d05121c424c4660fc7e","tid":1701277,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b83c27abdad01e79c43b4f005f7a2a506dbaa8","tid":1701277,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"散仔衝鋒 大sir領功"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f6403bf576df66b6cdccc36634cfdebb96ca0a","tid":1701277,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"低B仔"},{"pid"